    I have never in my life met someone as endearing and beautiful
as you. I still can not believe how lucky I am.
    I can honestly say that you truly complete me. You make me a better person
and are my inspiration every day.
    I don't know what I would do without you, and I can't wait to spend the rest
of my life with you. I will spend every day trying to make you happy because
you deserve nothing less.